---
title: Mexican Tomato Soup with Crispy Tortilla Strips
description: This flavoursome bowl is our hearty take on a Mexican classic – tortilla soup! The best part of this winter warmer is the DIY chips. Enjoy the moreish baked tortillas as a crisp topping, or submerge them in the soup to soak up all the rich, spiced tomato flavour.
